OL,7,FWhen Nicholas Humphery-Smith took his
OL,8,Fson Michael on as a sales manager in
OL,9,Fhis memorabilia firm, he had high hopes
OL,10,Fit would help heal a family rift.
OL,11,FMichael was unemployed and he wanted to
OL,12,Fgive him a fresh start in life.
OL,14,F"He hadn't had a job for maybe 15
OL,15,Fyears," said Nicholas. "And I hadn't
OL,16,Fseen him for quite some time. So we
OL,17,Ftook him on and I said I think I can
OL,18,Fshow you how to do sales."
OL,3,C'I was scammed out of #40,000 ` I felt
OL,4,Csick to my stomach when I found out it
OL,5,Cwas my son'
